  "_comment": "true-up trues up ITSELF, MARKER-FREE. The command and agent-guidance surfaces are generated to meta/contract.json (steward) by `node meta/build-contract.mjs` from `true-up capabilities`; docs that restate them derive-facts-from those facts via `seed` below. The repo also declares document audiences and doc/code/release/local-CI dependencies that no parser can infer. Change a command contract -> `true-up --impact meta/contract.json#commands.<name>`; change agent guidance -> `true-up --impact meta/contract.json#agent_guidance.<name>`; inspect the whole case study with `true-up graph --json`. The public-surface zone keeps machine-local paths out.",
